WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.766 --> 00:00:04.533
Secretary Zhang, do you know him?

2
00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:06.900
Of course I know

3
00:00:06.966 --> 00:00:08.466
Let me tell you something.

4
00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:09.866
This Toad

5
00:00:09.866 --> 00:00:12.866
Write love letters to chase me in school

6
00:00:12.866 --> 00:00:15.866
It was a school joke.

7
00:00:19.733 --> 00:00:22.000
Jin Feng, I really like you

8
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:23.066
Be my girlfriend

9
00:00:23.066 --> 00:00:24.566
I will definitely make you happy.

10
00:00:24.566 --> 00:00:27.100
Xiaofeng, you are so charming

11
00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:29.400
Even our school is famous for being poor

12
00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:31.200
I'm willing to spend money to buy you flowers

13
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:32.500
Oh, come on.

14
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:33.633
Cut it out.

15
00:00:34.266 --> 00:00:37.000
Do you really want me to be your girlfriend?

16
00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:38.433
To the breeze

17
00:00:38.766 --> 00:00:40.600
I really like you.

18
00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:42.866
Then close your eyes

19
00:00:43.866 --> 00:00:46.066
Don't close your eyes, you can ask me to do anything

20
00:00:49.066 --> 00:00:50.666
Okay, you can open your eyes now.

21
00:00:50.666 --> 00:00:52.800
Breeze, what did you put on my head?

22
00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:53.666
Hey don't take it

23
00:00:53.866 --> 00:00:55.133
That's my best friend

24
00:00:55.133 --> 00:00:56.900
Something to give to his friend

25
00:00:56.933 --> 00:01:00.033
I admire you so much that I forwarded him to you.

26
00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:02.700
Didn't you say you love me very much?

27
00:01:02.766 --> 00:01:04.366
Then prove it to me.

28
00:01:04.366 --> 00:01:07.066
You frog from here to there.

29
00:01:07.066 --> 00:01:09.300
I promise to be your girlfriend

